Developer : Rovio
Publisher : Rovio
Screenshots : http://www.rovio.com/en/our-work/games/view/62/angry-birds-star-wars-ii

Resume : The Force is strong with this one. Get ready for Angry Birds Star Wars II - the epic follow-up to the #1 smash hit game! Based on the Star Wars movie prequels, use the Force for good against the greedy Pork Federation or choose a much arker path. That's right; for the first time ever you can 'Join the Pork Side' and play as the fearsome Darth Maul, Emperor Palpatine and many other favorites! 

Minimum requirements : 
OS: Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8
Processor: 1 GHz
Memory: 512 MB
Graphics: Any OpenGL 1.3 compatible device
Hard Drive: 70 MB

Installation
1. Launch Angry Birds All [UniCrack Offline] v1.3
2. Uncheck Make Backup.
3. Hit Patch and choose exe file of the game.
4. Hit Open. ---PATCHING DONE---
5. Close Patcher
6. Copy key from "key.txt"
7. Run game - Press Activate Full Game!
8. Paste key with Ctrl+V & hit Register.
9. Play!

Have FUN! 
Please seed & enjoy!
